Package: causalmetrics
Title: Utility Functions and New Methods for Empirical Causal Inference
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data cleaning utilities, descriptive table functions, diagnostics,
    and from-scratch estimation methods (Double ML, synthetic DiD) for applied
    empirical research. Attaching the package also attaches the standard
    empirical analysis toolkit (data.table, fixest, estimatr, broom,
    modelsummary, ggplot2).
